    dc:description "Figure 2. Schematic illustration of dorsal-spine morphology in: (a) Glyptothorax prionotos, CMK 16246, paratype, 60.2 mm SL; (b) most Indochinese congeners (G. porrectus, CMK 25460, paratype, 70.9 mm SL illustrated). Images not to scale." ;
